<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>إِلَّا تَنْصُرُوهُ <span class="c4">[التوبة: ٤٠]</span>.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَإِلَّا تَغْفِرْ لِي <span class="c4">[هود: ٤٧]</span>.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
